attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Generate telemetry model-driven configuration for Interface protocol on IOS XR. Server: 172.16.1.10, port: 5432, protocol: tcp, encoding: json."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group INTERFACE
  sensor-path telemetry-model-driven-oper:telemetry-model-driven/subscriptions/subscription/subscription/source-interface
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 172.16.1.10
    port 5432
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-INTERFACE
  sensor-group-id INTERFACE sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
